<span class="postbody">Lol, we're opening this up again? Haha... Well, I can honestly say that I've kicked this dead horse into dust =p .
<br />

<br />
My feelings about the spell being on vendors;  it should have been there in the first place!  I'm glad that it is now!
<br />

<br />
My feelings about how Sony handled the issue;  They screwed us who did raid or buy it!  When the spell was for sell for about 9 months as a dropped item at 20 to 75k depending on the time and server, they should not have just given it away like this!  It should have either done it gradually by up'ing the drop rates or making a quest for it or (my best choice) make the dropped version have a higher slow ability (i.e. 55 or 60 percent rather than just 50 percent) so that we who did raid or buy it don't feel so ripped off.  If you take that is was worth even at the lowest amount (i.e. 20k pp's), that's a kashek kitar (granted good buy though cuz the going rate is 25 to 30k) or a phase spider carapace and some nice rings or something.
<br />

<br />
What I'm trying to say is that it was not fair to those of us who did raid or buy it.  It takes a lot of effort for some people to put raids together to get stuff like this (i.e. some of us are not in uber guilds) or several nights pharming hg's, cyclops, etc.. for the pp's to buy it.
<br />

<br />
Anyhow, it's a dead horse, but these are my views on the subject:  .eol.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
